    "Concurrently, attributes-based proxy re-encryption is employed to ensure access control of medical data, and the auditor will identify any activity that affects the integrity of EHRs.",
    "Due to the auditable and tamper-proof nature of BCT, any entity that illegally manipulated EHRs would be held responsible based on the evidence of the proposed Proof-Chain.",
